{"tid":1637775,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三擺只有一個方法成功又贏盡民意","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:49:06.000Z","uid":313312,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b10f3218a45e00196d93a8ada37ac200fcfd4ee","tid":1637775,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被擺工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有邊個打工仔想返工，但點解次次不合作都俾人屌，因為你無令到佢地返唔到工，你只係令到佢地遲返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問心，有咩慘得過工又要返，但被人搞到遲到，老細隨時扣人工，係車到迫，仲要好多未訓醒企幾個鐘，你話燥唔燥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽有人講，就放工先搞交通，你咁樣唔會令大家早走，只會令大家走唔到。仲衰過搞人返工，情況就放工前幾個鐘打風，個個無車返屋企，比平時用多幾個鐘先走到，你話燥唔燥。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住每人打工都希望唔洗返工，而唔係遲返工！</span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"614c36fd36bece91f4ceedc7212e93e1a4a1ef4a","tid":1637775,"uid":254388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:46:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80665a26d02516a69b49426c6631a8e991ed12c5","tid":1637775,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"和理非上場<br />\n三罷，加罷交稅"},{"pid":"d04839d2f75961d082efd61c8dea2013d9dee640","tid":1637775,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"614c36fd36bece91f4ceedc7212e93e1a4a1ef4a","tid":1637775,"uid":254388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:46:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"自己生意就係，我聽返黎係好多人屌，搞到唔拖唔水，阻住哂，係就搞到唔洗返"},{"pid":"92ddb89ea04eef82377ac2ac90d3adc9d3b9b151","tid":1637775,"uid":254388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6784eb886fbbcb3b593effd14b606ba9a93b8039","tid":1637775,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid